  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 10</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> *</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 25 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 13 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 27</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You create a crimson, archaic symbol that leeches Chakra from nearby creatures. It cannot be placed on a moving object, and cannot be moved once placed, though it can be placed on a creature. You must have at least 20 Chakra when creating the seal, and once it is finished you are reduced to 1 Chakra.<br><br>Creatures with 2 or more Chakra coming within the seal's area must nake a Fortitude save (DC 15) each round or have 2 Chakra absorbed by the seal. The seal will not drain from creatures with the user's Chakra Signature. The seal can hold up to 100 Chakra, and can be detected by Sense Chakra, though its location cannot be discerned that way. A creature with the Chakra Vampire bloodline can absorb Chakra from the seal.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
